snippet.title: LawBreakers "Between Our Guns" Gameplay Trailer [Official]
snippet.description:
Sign up for Alpha NOW and show that there’s no place more dangerous than between YOUR guns --- http://www.lawbreakers.com

Beat gravity into submission in LawBreakers, an exhilarating new first-person shooter where even the laws of physics can be shattered, creating unprecedented gravity-based combat, resulting in an ever-evolving and bloody arena.

SIGN UP FOR ALPHA NOW --- http://www.lawbreakers.com 
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM --- http://bit.ly/LBWishlist 

Follow LawBreakers on Social!
Twitter: http://twitter.com/lawbreakers
Facebook: http://facebook.com/lawbreakers
